text: Jean-Yves Le Bouillonnec (born September 15, 1950) was a member of the National Assembly of France. He represented Val-de-Marne's 11th constituency from 2002 to 2017, as a member of the Socialiste, radical, citoyen et divers gauche. ==References== Category:1950 births Category:Living people Category:Socialist Party (France) politicians Category:Deputies of the 12th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Deputies of the 13th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Deputies of the 14th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic
title: Jean-Yves Le Bouillonnec
